<span> Restored and returned to the community the cottage "Peppino Impastato" in Cinisi, Palermitano, where on May 9, 1978> the political activist and journalist was murdered > by the Mafia. This morning the inauguration ceremony with the President of the Region, who announced the membership in free use of the site, symbol of the fight against crime, to the associations of the territory engaged in the safeguard of memory.&nbsp;</span>
<br At the ceremony were also the regional council member to the Cultural Heritage and the superintendent of Palermo, the prefect and the commissioner of Palermo, the extraordinary commissioner of the Municipality of Cinisi, the president of the regional commission Antimafia, numerous civil and military authorities, as well as the family of Impastato and the delegations of the institute including Cinisi and the plexus of Terrasini of the State High School of Partinico recently entitled to Peppino and Felicia. The President of the Region entertained himself with the students, addressing the issue of legality practised in the daily life, and addressed them an invitation to visit Palazzo d'Orléans.&nbsp;
The project of recovery of the property and surrounding land >- expropriated and entered into possession of the Region in 2020 - was drafted by the Superintendency of Cultural Heritage of Palermo. The work had been started in January 2023 and financed with resources from the Development and Cohesion Fund 2020-2024 > for an amount of one hundred and fifty thousand euros. To execute them the company Scancarello.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
<div </div
&nbsp;
With this intervention the Sicilian government wanted to save from the degradation > a place already declared of cultural interest, which has a strong evocative value, of testimony of civilization and of fight against crime, > making it an open space to citizens and stage of that "path of memory" in memory of the victims of mafia that so many visitors carry out in the name of legality. Specifically, the works concerned the consolidation of the masonry and the backdrop with the construction of a perimeter wasp and the existing plasters. The cleaning and integration of existing floors with stone shelves by Billiemi bocciardate, the installation of wooden frames, entrance doors and window compartments and the construction of the electrical system. With regard to the overhaul of the roofs, it has been provided to the remaking of the screed, to the waterproofing with mortar and to the restoration of the ceiling incannucciato a vista.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
Inside the stable, instead of the stone seat on which traces of blood were imprinted, he chose to make a parallelepiped in transparent polycarbonate. On the surface of one of the sides, a portion was manually wrinkled to symbolically fix those spots, with the intent of "cristallizing the absence".<br> &nbsp;
